EntityFrameWork
    Object Relational Mapper(ORM)
    Translates our code into SQL commands that update our tables in the database
SQLite 
    means we don't need to install a databse server and sql, like just uses a file to store our database.
Entity Framework Features
    Querying
    Change Tracking
    Saving
    Concurrency
    Transactions
    Caching
    Built-in conventions
    Configurations
    Migrations

Microsoft has provided a Framework called Entity Framework to automate all these database related activites for our application.

